quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  88,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  88,1,kya tumhe uss chhaa jaane wali aafat ki khabar pohanchi hai ?
  88,2,kuch chehray uss roz khauf zada hunge
  88,3,sakht mushaqqat kar rahay hunge
  88,4,"thakey jatay hunge, shadeed aag mein jhulas rahay hunge"
  88,5,kholtey hue chashmay ka pani inhen peenay ko diya jaye ga
  88,6,khaar daar sookhi ghaas ke siwa koi khana unn ke liye nah hoga
  88,7,jo nah mota kere nah bhook mitaye
  88,8,kuch chehray uss roz ba ronaqe hon ge
  88,9,apni car guzari par khush hunge
  88,10,aliiiii maqam jannat mein hon ge
  88,11,koi behooda baat wahan nah sunen ge
  88,12,uss mein chashmay rawan hunge
  88,13,uss ke andar onche musannaden hon gi
  88,14,saghar rakhay hue hon ge
  88,15,gayo takyon ki qatarain lagi hon gi
  88,16,aur nafees farsh bichay hue hon ge
  88,17,( yeh log nahi mantay ) to kya yeh avnton ko nahi dekhte ke kaisay banaye gay ?
  88,18,aasman ko nahi dekhte ke kaisay uthaya gaya ?
  88,19,pahoron ko nahi dekhte ke kaisay jamaye gay ?
  88,20,aur zameen ko nahi dekhte ke kaisay bichai gayi ?
  88,21,"acha to ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) nasiyaat kiye jao, tum bas nasiyaat hi karne walay ho"
  88,22,kuch un par jabar karne walay nahi ho
  88,23,Albata jo shakhs mun moray ga aur inkaar kere ga
  88,24,to Allah is ko bhaari saza day ga
  88,25,inn logon ko palatna hamari taraf hi hai
  88,26,phir inn ka hisaab lena hamaray hi zimma hai
